00:01:43.691 --> 00:01:45.957
It is the human capacity
to move between the worlds

00:01:45.957 --> 00:01:48.614
of what is and what could
be that marks the emergence

00:01:48.614 --> 00:01:51.017
of a particular evolutionary context

00:01:51.017 --> 00:01:55.024
and history for the
